PUPPET:

Powerful automation for your entire hybrid and cloud-native estates

Puppet is one of the oldest Ruby based system administrators friendly IT automation tool majorly used
to configure manage deploy and  tested various applications and services across your whole infrastructure.

-   Puppet comes with two deployment models: 
        Master Client Deployment Model
        Self-contained standalone deployment Model 

-   Language Used : Puppet DSL (Domain Specific Language)

-   The primary responsibility of puppet is to maintain defined state are sometimes called desired state

-   Puppet is written in Ruby and uses its own DSL (Domain Specific Language). a declarative language



Execution Flow : (Pull Based Deployment Model)

Facts - Agents Send datas such as IP Address, MAC address to Puppet Master
Catalogue - Configuration Changes needs to be applied on Agent Nodes
Reports - Agent Reports back to Master that given configuration is applied.
